	<td bgcolor="#DEDFDF" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"><img src="../ubb/icons/icon1.gif" alt="Post" border="0"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Vindi<br />
<br />
Start 6 sec early - I dont think I have ever seen Vindi aggro a cleric unless the cleric got too close.<br />
<br />
Mobs are different though - some have large heal aggro while others have none. Also, some have large proximity aggro while others dont care if you are right under their skin. Vindi seems to have some proximity aggro.<br />
<br />
Anyway - for Vindi - start the first CH 6 sec before impact. If Vindi aggros the cleric doing that then its a taunt problem because that doesnt happen to us ever.<br />
<br />
