	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"><img src="../ubb/icons/icon1.gif" alt="Post" border="0"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Greetings!<br />
<br />
A variety of tactics depending on the aggro model of the mob:<br />
<br />
Pre-casting (having the CH chain running before mob makes initial contact, ducking out at the 9 sec point if not engaged). Normally requires advanced aggro management (area effect taunt, fungus glands/bio orbs, etc) or a *very* range-sensitive mob.<br />
<br />
Send another Paladin! Initial heal is a Lay on Hands from a sacrifical paladin. Good if the mob is a "kill it quickly" mass engagement, or requires significant movement to close distance.<br />
<br />
Send another Ranger! Mob positioned by a ranger under weaponshield discipline while the CH chain starts up on main tank.<br />
<br />
Liberal use of Glamorous and Horrifying Vision buffs.<br />
<br />
------------------<br />
