	<font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Galavant</b></font><br>
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">LFG dammit!</font><br>
	<img src="avatar.php?userid=3335&dateline=1034510217" border="0" alt=""><p>
