	<a name="post66574"></a>
	
	<font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Qwenya</b></font><br>
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">Archon</font><br>
	<p>
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">Registered: Jan 2002<br>
